oc:kn_2f6dd76e a oc:Heuristic,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When selecting CLAUDE.md sections for a project" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Use only the sections relevant to the project. Not all sections (Commands, Architecture, Key Files, Code Style, Environment, Testing, Gotchas, Workflow) are needed for every project." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Over-documenting with irrelevant sections adds noise and reduces the signal-to-noise ratio for the agent." ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

oc:kn_9ae371e5 a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When choosing which template to apply" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Template types must match project structure: use Minimal for simple projects, Comprehensive for larger projects, Package/Module for monorepo sub-packages, and Monorepo Root for multi-package repositories." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Mismatched template complexity leads to either insufficient documentation or bloated files with empty sections." ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

oc:kn_d6f298de a oc:DesignPrinciple,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When generating or updating any CLAUDE.md file" ;
    oc:directiveContent "CLAUDE.md files must be concise (one line per concept), actionable (copy-paste ready commands), project-specific (document patterns unique to this project), and current (reflect actual codebase state)." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Generic or outdated documentation wastes tokens and misleads the agent; specificity and accuracy are essential for effective agent assistance." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_dc64549b a oc:AntiPattern,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When generating a CLAUDE.md from templates" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Never include placeholder content like '<command>' or '<path>' in the final CLAUDE.md output — all placeholders must be replaced with real project-specific values." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Leaving placeholders in output produces useless documentation that looks structured but conveys no actual information." ;
    oc:severityLevel "CRITICAL" .

oc:kn_f17c3036 a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:Standard ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When updating an existing CLAUDE.md file" ;
    oc:directiveContent "When updating any CLAUDE.md: use actual file paths and real commands, verify info against the actual codebase, keep one line per concept, and ask 'would this help a new Claude session understand the project?'" ;
    oc:hasRationale "Ensures documentation remains accurate, concise, and genuinely useful rather than aspirational or generic." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

